         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne bot. &amp; zool Garden, ¶ 7. Dec. 1860 ¶ My dear Capt. Standish. ¶  ¶ I consulted with Mr Ang. M'Millan last night respecting the requirements for our journey to the Baw Baw Ranges. ¶ Angus McMi...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">60.12.07</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Frederick Standish</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Unit 3, VPRS 1199 inward correspondence, VA 724 Victoria Police, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne bot. &amp; zool Garden,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">7. Dec. 1860</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Capt. Standish.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I consulted with Mr Ang. M'Millan last night respecting the requirements for our journey to the Baw Baw Ranges.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Angus McMillan. See M to F. Standish, 6 December 1860.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>We think that it would be advantageous to have<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">five</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>horses in addition to those, which are available in my own establishment, and I was therefore anxious to wait on you to day to solicit your interest in getting them from your department on loan.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Quiet horses accustomed to the tether would be the most advantageous for our purpose, as we will not be able to secure them throughout the journey otherwise.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have here the requisite saddles, but I am in want of both tether roaps<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>ropes?</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>&amp; hobbles, &amp; some bridles. As such are probably not available in your department,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I will secure them myself</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Whilst thanking you for your friendly offer to aid us, I promise, that nothing shall be neglected to secure the safety of the horses entrusted to us &amp; that they shall be returned uninjured to you.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M to R. Heales,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>10 December 1860 and notes thereto.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Very regardfully,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>dear Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>yours</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd Mueller</p>
         </div>
